data.description: What are you waiting for? Get that loving feeling with Country living on almost 5 acres in Cantonment! Only 10 minutes to Nine Mile Rd Restaurants & Shops, 15 minutes to I-10, 30 minutes to Downtown life. Amazing Brick 4 BR/2 Bath home with metal roof and porches on front & back overlooking the property. Covered carport side entrance for two cars. Updated with new Wood flooring, fresh paint, new interior doors, Dishwasher, HVAC, 50 gallon Hot Water Heater, and an Outdoor Building with finished walls with a front porch that includes electric & A/C.  Additional parking pad and covered areas on each side of building.  A two-sided fireplace separates the home's two living areas. Master bathroom has jetted tub and a separate shower, Closets by Design has upgraded the dressing room. Kitchen has Beautiful & plentiful Oak Cabinets for all your cooking storage needs. Split floor plan for adult privacy. New barn door to amply-sized laundry room with a floor drain.  No HOA, room for all your adult & kid toys!  Plenty of space for your freedom to do as you please with your own land (farming, homesteading, a casita, pet breeding...), let your imagination run wild!
